Welcome to Dry Powder. I=E2=80=99m Bill Cohan. Congrats to my Dukies on
an exciting win last night at the Dean Dome at UNC=E2=80=94and now it=E2=80=
=99s on to Charlotte for the ACC Tournament, where hopefully this amazing t=
eam can continue its winning ways.

Tonight, I consider the antics of the Trump crypto bros, starting with Davi=
d Sacks, the entrepreneur and investor and podcaster influencer who has rem=
ade himself as Trump=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Ccrypto czar.=E2=80=9D Is Trump=E2=
=80=99s decision to create a Fort Knox=E2=80=93style Strategic Bitcoin Rese=
rve =E2=80=9Crat poison squared,=E2=80=9D as
Warren Buffett once suggested, or a rare sane policy emanating from the new=
